n【逆權運動】將軍澳刀手斬傷3男女 一度潛逃內地 下午羅湖返港被捕 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190820/59950983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F59950983&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=4bb2343e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F59950983&h=4a6c09d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190820/59950983</a><br />\n<br />\n【01:00】2女1男事主在隧道內與刀手聊天，其間刀手因政見不合，突然用刀斬傷3人，有目擊市民報警。刀手逞兇後逃去，有街坊尾隨，目睹刀手進入頌明苑嘉明閣。3名受傷事主送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n【01:24】刀手乘嘉明閣升降機到21樓，棄置染血衣服，換上紅色新衫後離開屋苑。約10分鐘後，警方抵達現場，並封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【02:00】警方撿獲兩把利刀，但被指未有向目擊者錄取口供，亦沒有查看大廈CCTV，亦沒有作大規模搜索，逗留約10分鐘後便收隊離開。 </strong></span><br />\n--------------------------------------------<br />\n好記得當時睇直播睇到燥, 黑警收隊, 之後街坊自己掃樓掃到21樓垃圾筒有物證, 再叫返黑警返黎, 黑警先肯開CCTV睇<br />\n<br />\n點解咁撚多私了, 大家係咪唔記得左原因?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50018a321e0ee5bfd8f08197d999034164a8141","tid":1821551,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:51:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb20936ccfbed89c61a4d12320d520f8eab85bcb","tid":1821551,"uid":23385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"483aa17ca3c36e4542c583e64f1f1359eb2688f8","tid":1821551,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"johnny係嗰條民意四眼仔？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"隻隻四眼狗都似樣"}],"pinned":{"pid":"945633056840e63123baa091f31a53db44daa0f7","tid":1821551,"uid":21248,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PM3wFOo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPM3wFOo.png&h=da632c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.c